        "de158e68-5d0d-4819-a625-e2dabdff87d1": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Product Details",
            "heading_size": "small",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Experience the benefits of Grounding with Terra Grounding Sheets. Made from <strong>95% organic premium cotton and 5% conductive silver woven fabric</strong>, these sheets are designed to bring comfort and health benefits to your nightly rest.<br/><br/><strong>How These Sheets Work:</strong><br/><br/>Grounding connects your body to the Earth’s natural energy. By plugging the included grounding cable into your wall’s grounding outlet, you link the sheets to the Earth, helping to neutralize excess electrical charges in your body. This process can clear away the electrical clutter that disrupts your body’s natural balance.<br/><br/><strong>Key Benefits:</strong></p><p><br/><strong>Better Sleep</strong>: Grounding while you sleep can help you wake up feeling refreshed and rejuvenated.<br/><br/><strong>Reduce Inflammation</strong>: The grounding connection may help in reducing inflammation, promoting overall health.<br/><br/><strong>Soft and Durable</strong>: These sheets are incredibly soft and stay that way, even after 100 wash cycles.<br/><br/>Terra Grounding Sheets bring the benefits of grounding into your home, helping you sleep better and wake up feeling your best.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_RDaXPM": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What's In the Package?",
            "heading_size": "medium",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>You’ll receive the following items with each purchase of our Grounding product:<br/><br/>1x Terra Grounding Product<br/>1x Connecting Cord (designed to connect directly to the grounding port of US outlets)</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_TdYymG": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Care & Dimensions",
            "heading_size": "medium",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Care:</p><p>It is good to wash your grounding sheets as it will not be harmed by washing. As a matter of fact, washing your sheets keeps it fresh and rids of all body sweats and nasties that may linger on your sheets from excessive usage!<br/><br/>Make sure to wash in a washing machine in warm water and in the case of using a tumble drier, to keep it on low gentle heat.<br/><br/>However, please keep in mind that bleaches or oils can damage the silver threads which assist in the grounding potential of your sheets, so we'd refrain from using those.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_RkbTyh": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Shipping Info",
            "heading_size": "medium",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Once an order is confirmed, it will be processed by our fulfillment team for processing and shipping. After your order is shipped, you will receive an email containing a tracking number and link.<br/><br/>The current processing time for orders is 1 business days.<br/><br/>For standard shipping delivery, the estimated times are America & Canada: 4-12 business days.<br/><br/></p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
